        <p>In the hands of an engaged educator, technology is a tool that can open a window to a wealth of knowledge and opportunity. It creates a learning environment that can grab each students attention and open their eyes to the true power of technology. The power to develop more than just their hand-eye coordination. The solution is having the right formula of technology to create that experience.
          <ul>
            <li>Creates an interactive learning experience
            <li>More opportunities for one-to-one teaching
